{"type":"data","nodes":[{"type":"data","data":[{"debug":1},true],"uses":{}},{"type":"data","data":[{"zotero":1,"inscriptions":5},{"title":2,"date":3,"citation":4},"Sicile","1896","\u003Cspan>Paolo Orsi, « Sicile », \u003Ci>Bulletin de Correspondance Hellénique\u003C/i> 20 (1896): 399‑400\u003C/span>",[6,106,157,227,278,329],{"file":7,"uri":7,"title":8,"status":9,"editionAuthor":11,"type":12,"objectType":16,"material":20,"condition":24,"layoutDesc":25,"handNote":32,"date":46,"places":51,"geo":60,"country":64,"region":65,"settlement":66,"repository":67,"idno":71,"textLang":74,"provenance":53,"letterHeights":78,"publications":79,"zotero":83,"keywords":87,"html":98,"bibl":99},"ISic001869","Funerary inscription for Artemo",{"_":10},"edited",null,{"_":13,"ana":14,"ref":15},"funerary","#function.funerary","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html",{"_":17,"ana":18,"ref":19},"block","#object.block","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/189.html",{"_":21,"ana":22,"ref":23},"limestone","#material.stone.limestone","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html","",{"layout":26},{"p":27,"rs":28,"damage":24},"Three lines of Greek letters, seemingly not centered / regularly laid out.",{"_":29,"ana":30,"ref":31},"chiselled","#execution.chiselled","http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1",{"lettering":33,"dimensions":34},"Described by Orsi (1896) as 'scritto a pessimi caratteri', and (1899) as 'lettere cattive, rustiche cosi che a tutta prima sembrano archaiche, e molto sconservate... L'iscrizione negligentemente redatta e scolpita è funebre di tarda età'. Pace states 'lettere del III sec. av. Cr.', but given the presence of lunate epsilon and Orsi's comments, a later date seems much more likely.",[35,42],{"type":36,"l":37,"from":38,"to":39,"h":40,"unit":41},"letterHeight","Line 1-3","line1","line3","55-95","mm",{"type":43,"l":44,"from":38,"to":45,"unit":41},"interlinear","Interlineation line 1 to 2","line2",{"_":47,"notBefore":48,"notAfter":49,"eviden